==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Yearling
<hw>Year"ling</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Year</ets> +
<ets>-ling</ets>.]</ety> <def>An animal one year old, or in the second
year of its age; -- applied chiefly to cattle, sheep, and
horses.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Yearling</ent>⟦br⟧

